<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Your Order - Aesthé</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and base styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header styles - just a placeholder as you mentioned you already have this */
        .header {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }

        /* Thank you section styles */
        .thank-you-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto 60px;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .thank-you-heading {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333333;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .thank-you-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .membership-info {
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .hide-confirmation-btn {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-transform: none;
        }

        .hide-confirmation-btn:hover {
            background-color: #333333;
        }

        .return-policy-link {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333333;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .return-policy-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Email highlight style */
        .email-highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Responsive styles */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .thank-you-container {
                padding: 30px 15px;
                margin: 15px auto 40px;
            }

            .thank-you-heading {
                font-size: 28px;
            }

            .thank-you-message,
            .membership-info {
                font-size: 14px;
                padding: 0 10px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .thank-you-heading {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .thank-you-message,
            .membership-info {
                font-size: 13px;
            }

            .hide-confirmation-btn {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 13px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Thank You Section -->
    <div class="thank-you-container">
        <h1 class="thank-you-heading">Thank You!</h1>

        <p class="thank-you-message">
            We are getting started on your order right away, and you will receive an order
            confirmation email shortly to <span class="email-highlight"><%=user.email%></span>. In the meantime,
            explore the latest fashion and get inspired by new trends, just head over to
            <a href="/" class="email-highlight">AESTHE</a>
        </p>

        <p class="membership-info">
            AESTHE members earn points on every purchase and have access to fashionable
            rewards and special perks. If you're a member, it may take up to 24 hours for
            your new points to be updated.
        </p>

        <a href="/orders">
            <button class="hide-confirmation-btn">TAP TO VIEW ORDER DETAILS</button>
        </a>
        <div>
            <a href="/shop" class="return-policy-link">Continue shopping with Aesthe</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="header">
        <img src="images/AestheLogo-red.png" alt="Aesthé Logo">
    </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>